{"tid":2105574,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 無懼國安惡法 立會35+過首關 61萬人投票反抗","createTime":"2020-07-12T17:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T06:54:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"23ab5a450a6c79142531e6e2af20e1fbbdb97dc5","tid":2105574,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/109044881_10159250941767448_8571055835432723250_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=U9WgwJ0EF6AAX9JSk3V&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=71b9a3ff8fa8f765e97d547911c0d328&amp;oe=5F318E94\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F109044881_10159250941767448_8571055835432723250_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DU9WgwJ0EF6AAX9JSk3V%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D71b9a3ff8fa8f765e97d547911c0d328%26oe%3D5F318E94&h=26f7404c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港蘋果日報<br />\n&middot; 10 mins &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【#A1頭條】民主陣營初選結束，61萬人再次為香港創造歷史，無懼國安法恐嚇和政權打壓，以票明志，締造歷史，自由揀選屬意的「正選球員」，為9月立會選舉爭取「35+」完成第一關。負責統籌初選的港大法律學院副教授戴耀廷直認投票人數遠超預期，「我嘅眼鏡唔知碎咗幾多次」；又稱投票意義超越尋找選舉代表，「係大家唔驚威嚇透過選票發聲」。政治學者認為，破紀錄的初選投票人數反映市民去年至今對政權的不滿，以選票呈現抗爭意志仍然堅定和對香港的感情，並預料民主派支持者較去年區選有所上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.10150161306277448/10159250941762448/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.10150161306277448%2F10159250941762448%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZos5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=8f81500f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.10150161306277448/10159250941762448/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"6467347483beeaf907a79af64b21153f3fa79ceb","tid":2105574,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" c